{"tid":1367692,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實避橡膠子彈唔難","createTime":"2019-07-26T10:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T14:29:04.000Z","uid":150100,"like":68,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"dbd8cf79b9753d2543ea5a4d77ac3962f01ba041","tid":1367692,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:32:16.000Z","msg":"最緊要係預判到同反應快<br />\n你喺佢手指掂個板機嘅前一刻向右跳<br />\n然後再即刻向左跳，咁佢就miss咗第一槍<br />\n之後你再即刻向前翻滾，拉近距離<br />\n之後嗰次就真係向你第一下個方向跳<br />\n個差佬會以為你今次用返上一次條橋<br />\n向另一個方向射，結果miss埋第二槍<br />\n你又有空檔再拉近距離<br />\n如果仲未夠近制服個差佬，唔緊要<br />\n教埋你避第三、四槍嘅方法<br />\n就係唔使避<br />\n因為依個時候個差佬嘅神經已經開始錯亂<br />\n佢好大機會會向曬你嘅左右方連開兩槍<br />\n所以打直向前衝就啱<br />\n如果你打開籃波就仲好<br />\n佢一放隻手指喺個板機度你就即做個碎步<br />\n扮向左右兩邊其中一邊避<br />\n避埋依兩槍你基本上已經喺可以制服佢嘅範圍內<br />\n就可以一舉制服佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb84a243adc79dbffbf919fb49f121b301a567c","tid":1367692,"uid":150100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:33:55.000Z","msg":"覺得有用嘅記得正皮同share俾其他手足睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4bdd7ad6355ba37127455de62031f4bb07d7c7b","tid":1367692,"uid":99700,"like":109,"dislike":0,"score":109,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DNjO0sZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDNjO0sZ.gif&h=c1fc2b07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81dbbaa2edb672db812ffd2090df8869515f7cfc","tid":1367692,"uid":150100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9edcc72fe9a8963fcf2d1cced74e7153a0de240","tid":1367692,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:40:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /